Note: Configuration Access Helpers

Let DefaultConfig be create_default_config[]
Let DevelopmentConfig be create_development_config[]
Let ProductionConfig be create_production_config[]
Let ResearchConfig be create_research_config[]

Note: Export the main configuration for use by other modules
Process called "get_default_config" returns DecisionConfig:
    Return DefaultConfig

Process called "get_config_for_algorithm" that takes algorithm_name as String returns AlgorithmConfig:
    Let config be get_default_config[]
    If config.algorithm_configs contains algorithm_name:
        Return config.algorithm_configs[algorithm_name]
    Return create_game_theory_config[]  Note: Default fallback